This folder contains environment files for installing a local Python environment. Note that the `morphology-game' example also uses TensorFlow, which has more installation options. Please visit the TensorFlow developer's website for up-to-date installation instructions.

To install the environments, use `venv` on Linux as follows:

```
python3 -m venv data-env
source data-env/bin/activate
pip3 install -r requirements.txt
```

